&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own a portfolio of specialty accounts, driving high retention and expansion revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Quarterly Business Reviews (QBRs) focused on delivering clinical and financial ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify growth opportunities and expand Phamily’s footprint across various practice departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise clients on workflow optimization and care management strategies to ensure adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex data into clear, actionable insights for clinical and operational leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify partnership risks and drive creative solutions to maintain account health.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product and marketing teams to share client feedback and influence the roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use HubSpot and AI tools to manage accounts efficiently and strategically.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
