&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Intelligence &amp;amp; Data Analytics Intern (Undergraduate&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location: Hybrid remote, 3-days in NY office&lt;br&gt;Job Type: Full-Time (ASAP - August 14th, 2026)&lt;br&gt;Job Reports To: Director of Business Intelligence&lt;br&gt;Salary Range: $25.00-$35.00/hr.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Jaan Health/Phamily&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jaan Health is a leading AI-based care management company serving healthcare providers. For nearly a decade, the company has leveraged its easy-to-use, proprietary technology to enable health systems, medical groups, and ACOs to deliver high-quality, high-ROI proactive care to hundreds of thousands of previously underserved patients.&lt;/p&gt;
