&lt;p&gt;Care managers play a vital role in this mission. Phamily helps care managers identify which patients need attention, guide outreach, and reduce the busywork so they can focus on what matters most: supporting people. Every day, care teams help patients feel seen, cared for, and connected to their health, while being part of a company that values compassion and measurable impact.&lt;/p&gt;
